snippet.title: REKNUM Fantasy of Dreams Kickstarter trailer
snippet.description:
Our #kickstarter campaign Reknum 2 for the #NES #SegaGenesis and #NintendoSwitch is now live! Face the fears from your dreams,become a hero or villain...  everything is up to you! The kingdom needs you!

Kickstarter here:
